{"title_page": "Pueblo, Colorado", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info ---------------->\n|name                     = Pueblo, Colorado\n|native_name              = <!-- for cities whose native name is not in English -->\n|nickname                 = Home of Heroes, Steel City\n|settlement_type          = City\n|motto                    = \"A City Of Excellence\"<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.pueblo.us/ |title= Official Website of Pueblo Colorado|publisher= Official Website of Pueblo Colorado |accessdate= September 22, 2012}}</ref>\n<!-- images and maps ----------->\n|image_skyline            = John Wark - Pueblo Riverwalk at Night.jpg\n|image_caption            = [[Arkansas River]] Walk in Pueblo\n|image_flag               = Flag of Pueblo, Colorado.gif\n|flag_size                =\n|image_seal               =\n|seal_size                =\n|image_shield             =\n|shield_size              =\n|blank_emblem_type        =\n|image_map                = File:Pueblo County Colorado Incorporated and Unincorporated areas Pueblo Highlighted 0862000.svg\n|mapsize                  = 250px\n|map_caption              = Location of Pueblo in Pueblo County, Colorado.\n|pushpin_map              = Colorado#USA\n|pushpin_map_caption      = Location within Colorado##Location within the United States\n|pushpin_label            = Pueblo, Colorado\n|pushpin_label_position   =\n|pushpin_relief           = yes\n|mapsize1                 =\n|map_caption1             = Location of Pueblo in the state of Colorado##Location of Pueblo in the United States\n|image_dot_map            =\n|dot_mapsize              =\n|dot_map_caption          =\n|dot_x                    =\n|dot_y                    = <!-- Location ------------------>\n|subdivision_type         = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name         = {{USA}}\n|subdivision_type1        = [[U.S. state|State]]\n|subdivisi